---
import BaseLayout from '~/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Usman Ramzan - DevOps Engineer & CTO"
  description="Senior DevOps Engineer and CTO at Urnlabs. Kubernetes expert, cloud architect, and agentic workflow pioneer."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-personal-hero">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-black/50 to-transparent"></div>
      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl">
          <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12">
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
                Muhammad
                <span class="block text-white/90">Usman Ramzan</span>
              </h1>
              <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-white/80 sm:text-xl">
                Senior DevOps Engineer & CTO at Urnlabs. 
                Building cloud-native infrastructure and AI agent workflows.
              </p>
              <div class="mt-10 flex items-center gap-x-6">
                <a
                  href="/contact"
                  class="rounded-md bg-white px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-black shadow-sm hover:bg-gray-100 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white transition-colors"
                >
                  Get in Touch
                </a>
                <a
                  href="/projects"
                  class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white hover:text-gray-200 transition-colors"
                >
                  View Projects <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <img
                class="h-64 w-64 rounded-full object-cover ring-4 ring-white/20"
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=400&h=400&fit=crop&crop=face"
                alt="Muhammad Usman Ramzan"
              />
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Current Focus Section -->
    <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:text-center">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold leading-7 text-accent-blue">Current Focus</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
            What I'm working on
          </p>
          <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
            Currently leading technical initiatives at Urnlabs while consulting on cloud infrastructure and DevOps transformations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-2xl sm:mt-20 lg:mt-24 lg:max-w-4xl">
          <dl class="grid max-w-xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-10 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-y-16">
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
                <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-accent-blue">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5.25 14.25h13.5m-13.5 0a3 3 0 01-3-3V6a3 3 0 013-3h13.5a3 3 0 013 3v5.25a3 3 0 01-3 3m-16.5 0a3 3 0 003 3h13.5a3 3 0 003-3m-16.5 0h16.5" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                CTO at Urnlabs
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                Leading technical strategy for AI agent platforms. Building governance-first infrastructure for enterprise automation.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
                <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-signal-green">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 15a4.5 4.5 0 004.5 4.5H18a3.75 3.75 0 001.332-7.257 3 3 0 00-3.758-3.848 5.25 5.25 0 00-10.233 2.33A4.502 4.502 0 002.25 15z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Cloud Architecture
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                Designing multi-cloud Kubernetes platforms on EKS, OKE, and RKE2. Focus on security, scalability, and cost optimization.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
                <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-purple-600">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.75 3.104v5.714a2.25 2.25 0 01-.659 1.591L5 14.5M9.75 3.104c-.251.023-.501.05-.75.082m.75-.082a24.301 24.301 0 014.5 0m0 0v5.714c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591L19.8 15.3M14.25 3.104c.251.023.501.05.75.082M19.8 15.3l-1.57.393A9.065 9.065 0 0112 15a9.065 9.065 0 00-6.23-.693L5 14.5m14.8.8l1.402 1.402c1.232 1.232.65 3.318-1.067 3.611A48.309 48.309 0 0112 21c-2.773 0-5.491-.235-8.135-.687-1.718-.293-2.3-2.379-1.067-3.611L5 14.5" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Agentic Workflows
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                Pioneering deterministic AI agent workflows with DAG orchestration and real-time governance controls.
              </dd>
            </div>
            <div class="relative pl-16">
              <dt class="text-base font-semibold leading-7">
                <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-orange-600">
                  <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                Security & Compliance
              </dt>
              <dd class="mt-2 text-base leading-7 text-gray-300">
                Implementing zero-trust architectures with policy-as-code governance. SOC2 and enterprise compliance expertise.
              </dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Featured Content Section -->
    <section class="bg-gray-900 py-24 sm:py-32">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl lg:mx-0">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">Latest Writing & Projects</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
            Thoughts on DevOps, cloud architecture, and AI automation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="mx-auto mt-10 grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10 sm:mt-16 sm:pt-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-3">
          <!-- Placeholder for featured posts/projects -->
          <article class="flex max-w-xl flex-col items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs">
              <time class="text-gray-400">Recent</time>
              <span class="relative z-10 rounded-full bg-accent-blue px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-white">DevOps</span>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative">
              <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 group-hover:text-accent-blue transition-colors">
                <a href="/writing">
                  <span class="absolute inset-0"></span>
                  Kubernetes Platform Engineering at Scale
                </a>
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-5 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
                Building multi-tenancy Kubernetes platforms with GitOps, service mesh, and comprehensive observability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="flex max-w-xl flex-col items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs">
              <time class="text-gray-400">Recent</time>
              <span class="relative z-10 rounded-full bg-signal-green px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-white">AI</span>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative">
              <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 group-hover:text-signal-green transition-colors">
                <a href="/projects">
                  <span class="absolute inset-0"></span>
                  Urnlabs Platform Architecture
                </a>
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-5 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
                Designing and implementing the technical infrastructure for enterprise AI agent workflows.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
          <article class="flex max-w-xl flex-col items-start justify-between">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-x-4 text-xs">
              <time class="text-gray-400">Recent</time>
              <span class="relative z-10 rounded-full bg-purple-600 px-3 py-1.5 font-medium text-white">Speaking</span>
            </div>
            <div class="group relative">
              <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-semibold leading-6 group-hover:text-purple-400 transition-colors">
                <a href="/talks">
                  <span class="absolute inset-0"></span>
                  Cloud-Native Security Patterns
                </a>
              </h3>
              <p class="mt-5 line-clamp-3 text-sm leading-6 text-gray-300">
                Conference talk on implementing zero-trust security in Kubernetes environments.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="bg-primary-bg">
      <div class="px-6 py-24 sm:px-6 sm:py-32 lg:px-8">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
            Let's work together
          </h2>
          <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-gray-300">
            Available for consulting on cloud infrastructure, DevOps transformation, and AI platform architecture.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-x-6">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="rounded-md bg-accent-blue px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-white shadow-sm hover:bg-blue-500 transition-colors"
            >
              Start a Conversation
            </a>
            <a
              href="/resume"
              class="text-sm font-semibold leading-6 text-white hover:text-accent-blue transition-colors"
            >
              Download Resume <span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>